{"tid":2428494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因應共軍侵擾 台灣國軍在東沙島實彈射擊訓練","createTime":"2021-03-01T14:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T05:25:43.000Z","uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd43d12fdaa9fc29dc94a635505913ad98e5cb4","tid":2428494,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">因應共軍侵擾 東沙島9日實彈射擊訓練</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/03/01 22:05<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20210301/1200x797_604927465281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20210301%2F1200x797_604927465281.jpg&h=6adf2f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對共機常態化侵擾台灣西南防空識別區，根據海巡署射擊通報，東沙島1日及9日進行第一季火砲對海實彈射擊。圖為過去東沙島海巡官兵戰備演練情形。（中央社檔案照片）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者游凱翔台北1日電）<span class=\"red\">面對共機常態化侵擾台灣西南防空識別區（ADIZ），海巡官兵持續加強戰備，根據海巡署射擊通報，東沙島今天及9日進行今年第一季火砲對海實彈射擊，藉此模擬各類情況。</span><br />\n<br />\n國防部「即時軍事動態」刊載，共軍近年頻以包括慢速機、戰機在內等各型軍機，侵擾台灣西南防空識別區，不止曾多次逾越台灣海峽中線；且根據航跡圖，曾數度接近屬中華民國領土的東沙群島，已造成區域和平穩定的緊張。<br />\n<br />\n日本共同社去年5月曾報導，共軍在中國海南島海域進行軍演，目的是演練奪取東沙群島，引起外界關注；當時國防部回應，國軍都能掌握敵情動態，有應處機制、應援計劃，國軍基於國安，包括東沙島、太平島在內的外島離島，都會強化戰備。<br />\n<br />\n為了加強戰備，據行政院海洋委員會海巡署日前公告的射擊通報，<span class=\"red\">東沙島今天及9日在附近海域進行今年第一季火砲對海實彈射擊，演練時間為每天上午8時至晚上9時止，最大彈道高度為1萬2000呎。</span><br />\n<br />\n東沙島、南沙太平島上的防務，均由海軍陸戰隊代訓的海巡官兵負責駐守，但國防部去年6月證實，海軍陸戰隊將短期派駐東沙島，目的是提升海巡防衛能力。（編輯：林興盟）1100301<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103010211.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202103010211.aspx&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=2d4a1541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103010211.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"bec1907a0769ee79130d6fed8e38ec22d7bb67ce","tid":2428494,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LMGm71Uy7IE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLMGm71Uy7IE&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=28c5a518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LMGm71Uy7IE</a>"},{"pid":"ba83164296e8f33cc77b87cf9ef6e87c89ac34ed","tid":2428494,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FMXw0ACw8-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFMXw0ACw8-A&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=9ab9276d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FMXw0ACw8-A</a>"},{"pid":"8669e856d00efa4a198e1649d4885e99143963bc","tid":2428494,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:01:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/76PsRiq0IQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F76PsRiq0IQc&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d77e2e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/76PsRiq0IQc</a>"},{"pid":"3fe00e27ff465a9cd23667900dd1a286d2257bf4","tid":2428494,"uid":226955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">一個中國<br />\n中華民國</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"38c55f60e62f82f71eaa155ebfa1a3730ef26781","tid":2428494,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v7c4ZP-Z3nI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv7c4ZP-Z3nI&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=a0092d7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v7c4ZP-Z3nI</a>"},{"pid":"4ac0079cab28498081e374a68f3cac6d4764e63a","tid":2428494,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"睇錯係東沙島街"},{"pid":"bf1bec7e4a5c0da1859840f6eb1977a46b1301cd","tid":2428494,"uid":337052,"like":0,"